Interface GwtLogout

All Superinterfaces:
RemoteService
public interface GwtLogout
extends RemoteService

<logout> direct from GWT RPC,you need instantiate a GwtLogoutSuccessHandler and assign to <logout success-handler-ref="hander-reference"/>
This interface did not annotated with @RemoteServiceRelativePath, Do not generate instance by GWT.create, Just invoke GwtLogoutAsync.Util.getInstance instead.
使用GWT RPC進行登出，必須建立一GwtLogoutSuccessHandler實例， 並且指定到to <logout success-handler-ref="實例參照"/>
本界面並未標記@RemoteServiceRelativePath，所以不要用 GWT.create建立intance，請改用 GwtLogoutAsync.Util.getInstance
